    dc:creator "Chen, Jin-Min; Suwannapoom, Chatmongkon; Wu, Yun-He; Poyarkov, Nikolay A.; Xu, Kai; Pawangkhanant, Parinya; Che, Jing" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Integrative taxonomy reveals a new species of Leptobrachella (Anura: Megophryidae) from the mountains of northern Thailand" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568541>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568547>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568549>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568551>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568553>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568543>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568545> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568541>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Distribution of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. The known distribution of L. murphyi sp. nov. indicated by the purple dots (1: Type Locality Doi Inthanon, Thailand; 2: Doi Chiang Dao, Thailand)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568541/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568547>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Holotype of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. (KIZ034039) in life. (A) General dorso-lateral view, (B) dorsal view, (C) ventral view, (D) thenar view of the right hand, (E) plantar view of the right foot, (F) close-up of the iris. Photos by Chatmongkon Suwannapoom." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568547/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568549>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Type series of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. in preservation in dorsal and ventral aspects. Photos by Jin-Min Chen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568549/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568551>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Paratypes of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. in life in dorso-lateral (upper row) and ventral (lower row) aspects. A: KIZ034038; B: KIZ034158. Photos by Chatmongkon Suwannapoom." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568551/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568553>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Breeding habitat of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. at the type locality in Doi Inthanon, Chiang Mai Province, Thailand. Photo by Chatmongkon Suwannapoom." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568553/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568543>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bayesian phylogram of Leptobrachella inferred from 16S mtDNA gene fragment. “*” denotes high support by Bayesian posterior probabilities (BPP> 0.95), and bootstrap support values (BS> 70%); Nodes without any numbers or symbols represent low support values. Outgroup taxa not shown. Inserted photo showing Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. Scale bars represent the number of substitutions per site. New samples for the present study are indicated by the blue font." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568543/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5568545>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Advertisement call of Leptobrachella murphyi sp. nov. (A) A 15 s waveform of relative amplitude (Rel. amp.) of male KIZ034159 (recorded at ambient air temperature of 15.0 °C); (B) power spectrum (relative amplitude vs. frequency) and (C) the corresponding spectrogram of the same call; (D) expanded 1.2 s waveform of relative amplitude, (E) corresponding power spectrum and (F) spectrogram of the same call." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5568545/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

